title: Acqua Di Gioia by Giorgio Armani Eau De Parfum Spray for Women, 1.70-Ounce
description: Introduced in 2010, acqua di gioia contains notes including jasmine sambac, cedar, labdanum, aquatic green accord, peony, brown sugar accord, mint leaves, pink pepper, limone primo fiore.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Fair & White Dark Spot Remover
description: This new formula contains "F.A.W. Lightening" to lighten efficiently dark spots and pigment blemishes of the skin (scars, pregnancy, age spots, sun patches). The result is a strong bleaching effect for a smooth and clearer complexion free of brown patches. Manufactured and tested by the French Dermatological Laboratory. The Dark Spot Remover, because of its very high efficient formula, erases brown unsightly marks. Apply locally with a cotton swab.
